Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp.
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.206, 21. Nane, Aischinas. Alexandria, Greco-Roman Museum, MGR130.46 is from the same die.
